reviewText: I really liked most of the movie. There was only two things I did not care for: The "music videos" in the movie, they seem too out of place and the ending is just too much of a cop out, that is a terrible way to end the movie. That is why it kept me from giving it 5 stars.
Okay, should be part of my Prime membership
I enjoyed the movie however it could have been shorter in length and still been fine.  The actress did a great job in her role.
It's a long movie but enjoyable at a right price considering it's a import but great service.
